Spain Boosts Incentives to Coal, Gas Power Plants, Cinco Says

-- B y   E s t e b a n   D u a r t e
-- 
2011-06-09T06:09:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-09/spain-boosts-incentives-to-coal-gas-power-plants-cinco-says.html
Spain  plans to increase incentives
for  utility companies  operating coal and gas  power plants ,
 Cinco Dias  reported, citing a draft of a regulation to be passed
by the Industry Ministry.  The power plants will get a total of 1.1 billion euros
($1.6 billion), an increase of 600 million euros, the newspaper
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Esteban Duarte in Madrid at 
 eduarterubia@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Armstrong at 
 parmstrong10@bloomberg.net  